data.description: Beautiful Bella Vista Home less than 5 years old. This gently lived in home is the Claremore floor plan that offers 2177 sqft. No carpet throughout the first floor. Open floor plan that flows from the front door to the living area and kitchen. Huge kitchen island with plenty of cabinet space, granite countertops, and designer subway tile backsplash. All bedrooms upstairs and a bonus room. Oversized primary suite with dual vanities and a tub/shower combo. This home is also located on the largest lot in Meadow Park and offers an above ground pool. Located mins away from downtown, Fort Sam Houston, and shopping centers.
